# Theme Functions Setup

## Required Theme Support
```php
add_theme_support('title-tag');
add_theme_support('post-thumbnails');
add_theme_support('html5', array('search-form', 'comment-form', 'comment-list', 'gallery', 'caption'));
add_theme_support('automatic-feed-links');
```

## Register Navigation Menus
- Use `register_nav_menus()` to register menu locations
- Display with `wp_nav_menu()` in templates

## Register Widget Areas
- Use `register_sidebar()` for widget areas
- Display with `dynamic_sidebar('sidebar-name')` in templates

## Enqueue Assets
- Use `wp_enqueue_script()` and `wp_enqueue_style()` (never hardcode in templates)
- Hook into `wp_enqueue_scripts` action
- Version assets with theme version: `wp_get_theme()->get('Version')`
- Load scripts in footer when possible: 5th parameter `true`
- Use `wp_localize_script()` to pass data to JavaScript

## Other Setup
- `add_image_size()` for custom image sizes
- `load_theme_textdomain()` for translations
